Class StaffRepository

java.lang.Object
repository.Repository<HospitalStaff>
repository.user.StaffRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRepository<HospitalStaff>, Iterable<HospitalStaff>
public class StaffRepository extends Repository<HospitalStaff>
StaffRepository is a singleton class that manages the collection of HospitalStaff entities. It extends the Repository class and provides methods to load, retrieve, and iterate over the list of hospital staff members stored in a CSV file.
